of this same building.

64
00:08:56,102 --> 00:08:57,036
Right?

65
00:08:59,972 --> 00:09:01,674
That's why
you don't use the elevator.

66
00:09:01,974 --> 00:09:04,076
Who told you that?
How do you know it?

67
00:09:04,143 --> 00:09:05,177
