- No?

102
00:10:53,185 --> 00:10:54,253
Good morning.

103
00:10:54,320 --> 00:10:55,821
My sweetheart.

104
00:10:56,389 --> 00:10:59,925
Listen, I need to borrow
the money I told you about.

105
