138
00:13:21,967 --> 00:13:23,936
No, she's always had that temper.

139
00:13:25,604 --> 00:13:27,840
Listen. Go talk to him.

140
00:13:29,208 --> 00:13:31,310
Yes. Try to find out why he's here.

141
00:13:33,212 --> 00:13:34,146
Go.

142
