Someone might see us.

163
00:14:38,644 --> 00:14:40,646
Andrea, if this is not
the place, where?

164
00:14:41,714 --> 00:14:45,050
Because I'm tired
of hiding in the closet.

165
00:14:45,751 --> 00:14:48,487
