I don't want Matilde to get hurt.

1139
01:31:25,313 --> 01:31:26,247
Cheers.

1140
01:31:44,365 --> 01:31:46,868
Why didn't you tell me
Miguel is my father?

1141
01:31:47,602 --> 01:31:49,437
